name: birdsnest necklace
description:
This necklace has a beautiful little nest made from a large and small gauge of non-tarnish silver plated copper wire. The nest encloses three gorgeous cream-coloured freshwater pearls. 

This nest is hung on a silver chain and is accented with a silver feather charm.

The necklace measures 79.5cm. The nest, on average, has a diameter of 2.5cm. The feather measures 2.5cm.

Each necklace is slightly different due to the fact that the freshwater pearls are naturally made. Currently, the pearls are without the bump in the middle. The size of the feather and the shape of the pearls currently being used are pictured last.

name: birdsnest ring
description:
This ring has a beautiful little nest made from a large and small gauge of non-tarnish silver plated copper wire. The nest encloses three gorgeous cream-coloured freshwater pearls. 

This nest is hung on a silver coloured stainless steel adjustable ring base.

The nest, on average, has a diameter of 2.5cm. 

Each ring is slightly different due to the fact that the freshwater pearls are naturally made. Currently, the pearls are without the bump in the middle.

name: skeleton key bracelet
description:
This bracelet features a collection of five different silver skeleton keys on a silver chain. The clasp is a sterling silver toggle and a silver lock charm as the hoop.

It measures 19.5 cm long.


The name Cloelia comes from the latin 'clavis' (key), and 'claustra' (lock).

name: chain mail bracelet
description:
This simple bracelet features handmade byzantine chain mail made with silver jump rings.
A delicate silver feather charm hangs by the sterling silver toggle clasp.

The bracelet measures 18 cm long.

The name Brynja is an old Norse name derived from the word brynja, meaning "armor, coat of mail."

name: jellyfish bracelet
description:
This charm bracelet reminds me of little colourful jellyfish. It features many opalescent, milky cyclamen genuine Swarovski Bicone beads and many turquoise beads.

The bracelet itself is made from a sterling silver chain with a sterling silver toggle clasp.

It measures about 18.3cm long including the clasp.
